---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy | BrewYourBeing">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-28 pb-20 bg-brew-cream min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-brew-brown mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>
      <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p><strong class="text-brew-brown">Effective Date:</strong> February 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">1. Session Fees</h2>
        <p>All session fees are communicated at the time of booking confirmation. Payment is expected prior to or at the time of the session, as specified during the scheduling process.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">2. Cancellation by Client</h2>
        <p><strong>More than 24 hours before the session:</strong> Full refund or free rescheduling is available.</p>
        <p><strong>Less than 24 hours before the session:</strong> A cancellation fee of 50% of the session cost may apply. The remaining amount can be refunded or applied toward a future session.</p>
        <p><strong>No-show (without prior notice):</strong> No refund will be provided for missed sessions without prior notice.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">3. Cancellation by Therapist</h2>
        <p>In the rare event that a session needs to be cancelled by the therapist due to unforeseen circumstances, you will be offered a full refund or the option to reschedule at no additional cost.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">4. Package Sessions</h2>
        <p>If you have purchased a package of multiple sessions, refunds for unused sessions will be calculated based on the individual session rate minus any package discount that was applied. Refund requests for packages must be made within 90 days of purchase.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">5. Refund Processing</h2>
        <p>Approved refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days and will be returned to the original payment method. Please allow additional time for your bank or payment provider to reflect the refund.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">6. Exceptions</h2>
        <p>In cases of genuine emergencies or extenuating circumstances, refund requests will be reviewed on a case-by-case basis with empathy and understanding.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-brew-brown pt-4">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>For refund requests or questions about this policy, please reach out at <a href="mailto:brewyourbeing@gmail.com" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">brewyourbeing@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+916263121929" class="text-brew-light hover:text-brew-brown underline">+91 6263-121929</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-brew-brown hover:text-brew-light transition-colors font-medium">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
